        <num>CC 1997</num>
        <heading>1997.  Obligor in bad faith</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 1997.  Obligor in bad faith
An obligor in bad faith is liable for all the damages, foreseeable or not, that are a direct consequence of his failure to perform.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
